[Experimental] The SubjectSearch API returns all subjects that have a specific action (relation) on a given resource. This is useful for answering questions like "Who can read this document?" or "Who can administer this folder?"

Results can be filtered by subject type and support pagination for large result sets.

## Examples
### Find all users who can read a document
```json
{
  "resource": {"type": "document", "id": "roadmap"},
  "action": {"name": "can_read"},
  "subject": {"type": "user"}
}

